ntage-style frets provides a classic performance that is unique to the Traditional series. A vintage-style Sting-Through-Body bridge with three brass saddles, and the original pickups selected for the Traditional series produce realistic, musical vintage tones. The narrowly designed nut width makes it easy for Japanese players to play. Solid guitar craftsmanship and flexible answers to player needs are reflected in this series.\n\n* The image is a sample.\n\nSeries: Traditional\nBody Material: Ash\nBody Finish: Gloss Polyester\nNeck: Maple, “U” Shape\nNeck Finish: Gloss Urethane\nFingerboard: Maple, 9.5 ”(241 mm)\nFrets: 21, Vintage\nPosition Inlays: Black Dot (Maple)\nNut (Material / Width): Bone, 1.615 ”(41.02 mm)\nTuning Machines: Fender® Vintage “F” Stamped\nScale Length: 25.5 ”(648 mm)\nBridge: 3-Saddle Vintage-Style Tele® with Slotted Steel Saddles\nPickguard: 3-Ply Black\nPickups: Vintage-Style Single-Coil Tele® (Bridge), Fender® Wide Range Humbucking (Neck)\nPickup Switching: 3-Position Toggle: Position 1. Bridge Pickup, Position 2. Bridge and Neck Pickups, Position\n3. Neck Pickup\nControls: Volume 1. (Neck Pickup), Volume 2. (Bridge Pickup), Tone 1. (Neck Pickup), Tone 2.\n(Bridge Pickup)\nControl Knobs: Vintage-Style Skirted Black Plastic\nHardware Finish: Nickel / Chrome\nStrings: Nickel Plated Steel (.009-.042 Gauges)\n\nGig case included', 99000, '1038', 'a:3:{i:0;s:71:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/ikebe-rockhouse/cabinet/guitar/guitar01/671232.jpg\";i:1;s:71:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/ikebe-rockhouse/cabinet/guitar/imgrc0079062958.jpg\";i:2;s:71:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/ikebe-rockhouse/cabinet/guitar/imgrc0079062959.jpg\";}', '2021-09-04 02:40:01', '2021-09-04 19:46:52'),
(197, 3, 'https://item.rakuten.co.jp/jeugia/10015782/', 'Fender By Squier Classic Vibe 70s Telecaster DeluxeMaple Fingerboard Blackスクワイヤー テレキャスター エレキギター ギター ブラック', '70年代Telecasterの進化を、忠実に再現したモデルです。\n\n\nClassic Vibe 70s Telecaster Deluxe\n\n\nフェンダーデザインのワイドレンジなデュアルハムバッキングピックアップの搭載。ダイナミックなトーンを生み出します。滑らかで快適な9.5インチラジアスの指板とタイトなフレットを備え、プロファイルされたネック形状は、スリムで快適なC型タイプ。ブリッジは、ボディ裏に弦通しするヴィンテージスタイルです。\n\nBody Material：Poplar\nBody Finish：Gloss Polyurethane\nNeck：Maple, “C” Shape\nNeck Finish：Tinted Gloss Urethane\nFingerboard：Maple, 9.5” (241 mm)\nFrets：21, Narrow Tall\nPosition Inlays：Black Dots (Maple)\nNut (Material/Width)：Bone, 1.650” (42 mm)\nTuning Machines：Vintage-Style\nScale Length：25.5” (648 mm)\nBridge：3-Saddle Vintage-Style Strings-Through-Body TeleR with Chrome Barrel Saddles\nPickguard：3-Ply Black\nPickupsFenderR Designed Wide Range Humbucking (Bridge), N/A (Middle), FenderR Designed Wide Range Humbucking (Neck)\nPickup Switching：3-Position Toggle Position 1. Bridge Pickup, Position 2. Bridge and Neck Pickups, Position 3. Neck Pickup\nControls：Volume 1. (Neck Pickup), Volume 2. (Bridge Pickup), Tone 1. (Neck Pickup), Tone 2. (Bridge Pickup)\nControl Knobs：Skirted Amp Knobs\nHardware Finish：Nickel\n付属品：専用ソフトケース\n\n\n練習する際に必要なアンプなどもセットになって数量限定で絶賛販売中！\n\n\n\n\n◇詳しくはこちらをクリック\n\n\n夜間の練習にも最適なヘッドホンアンプセットも数量限定で絶賛販売中！\n\n\n\n\n◇詳しくはこちらをクリック\n\n※商品の汚れや状態はお問い合わせ下さい。\n※掲載の商品は店頭や他のECサイトでも並行して販売しております。在庫情報の更新には最大限の努力をしておりますが、ご注文が完了しましても売り切れでご用意できない場合がございます。\nその際はご注文をキャンセルさせていただきますので、予めご了承くださいませ。\nまた、お取り寄せ商品の場合、生産完了などの理由でご用意できない場合がございます。\n※お届け先が北海道や沖縄、その他離島の場合、「」と表記の商品であっても別途中継料や送料を頂戴いたします。その際は改めてご連絡を差し上げますのでご了承ください。', 'Fender By Squier Classic Vibe 70s Telecaster DeluxeMaple Fingerboard Black Squier Telecaster Electric Guitar Guitar Black', 'It is a model that faithfully reproduces the evolution of the 70\'s Telecaster.\n\n\nClassic Vibe 70s Telecaster Deluxe\n\n\nEquipped with a wide range dual humbucking pickup with a fender design. Produces a dynamic tone. With a smooth and comfortable 9.5 inch radius fingerboard and tight frets, the profiled neck shape is a slim and comfortable C-shaped type. The bridge is a vintage style with strings threaded through the back of the body.\n\nBody Material: Poplar\nBody Finish: Gloss Polyurethane\nNeck: Maple, “C” Shape\nNeck Finish: Tinted Gloss Urethane\nFingerboard: Maple, 9.5 ”(241 mm)\nFrets: 21, Narrow Tall\nPosition Inlays: Black Dots (Maple)\nNut (Material / Width): Bone, 1.650 ”(42 mm)\nTuning Machines: Vintage-Style\nScale Length: 25.5 ”(648 mm)\nBridge: 3-Saddle Vintage-Style Strings-Through-Body TeleR with Chrome Barrel Saddles\nPickguard: 3-Ply Black\nPickupsFenderR Designed Wide Range Humbucking (Bridge), N / A (Middle), FenderR Designed Wide Range Humbucking (Neck)\nPickup Switching: 3-Position Toggle Position 1. Bridge Pickup, Position 2. Bridge and Neck Pickups, Position 3. Neck Pickup\nControls: Volume 1. (Neck Pickup), Volume 2. (Bridge Pickup), Tone 1. (Neck Pickup), Tone 2. (Bridge Pickup)\nControl Knobs: Skirted Amp Knobs\nHardware Finish: Nickel\nAccessories: Dedicated soft case\n\n\nA limited number of amps required for practicing are also on sale!\n\n\n\n\n◇ Click here for details\n\n\nA limited number of headphone amplifier sets that are ideal for night practice are also on sale!\n\n\n\n\n◇ Click here for details\n\n* Please contact us for dirt and condition of the product.\n* The listed products are also sold in stores and on other EC sites in parallel. We make every effort to update the stock information, but even if the order is completed, it may not be available due to sold out.\nIn that case, please note that your order will be cancelled.\nIn addition, in the case of backordered products, we may not be able to prepare them due to reasons such as production completion.\n* If the delivery address is Hokkaido, Okinawa, or other remote islands, a separate relay fee and shipping fee will be charged even for products marked with \"\". In that case, please note that we will contact you again.', 59400, '623', 'a:12:{i:0;s:64:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/jeugia/cabinet/ibatraki/imgrc0073015626.jpg\";i:1;s:64:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/jeugia/cabinet/ibatraki/imgrc0073015627.jpg\";i:2;s:64:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/jeugia/cabinet/ibatraki/imgrc0073015628.jpg\";i:3;s:64:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/jeugia/cabinet/ibatraki/imgrc0073015629.jpg\";i:4;s:64:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/jeugia/cabinet/ibatraki/imgrc0073015630.jpg\";i:5;s:64:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/jeugia/cabinet/ibatraki/imgrc0073015631.jpg\";i:6;s:64:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/jeugia/cabinet/ibatraki/imgrc0073015632.jpg\";i:7;s:64:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/jeugia/cabinet/ibatraki/imgrc0073015633.jpg\";i:8;s:64:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/jeugia/cabinet/ibatraki/imgrc0073015634.jpg\";i:9;s:64:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/jeugia/cabinet/ibatraki/imgrc0073015635.jpg\";i:10;s:64:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/jeugia/cabinet/ibatraki/imgrc0073015636.jpg\";i:11;s:64:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/jeugia/cabinet/ibatraki/imgrc0073015637.jpg\";}', '2021-09-04 02:40:01', '2021-09-04 19:46:55'),
(198, 3, 'https://item.rakuten.co.jp/guitarplanet-online/fujigen-ntl10ral-swh/', 'FgN(FUJIGEN) NTL10RAL SWH 新品[フジゲン,富士弦][国産][White,ホワイト,白][Telecaster,テレキャスタータイプ][Electric Guitar,エレキギター]', '長い歴史と確かな品質で、世界のギター工場と呼ばれたフジゲン。\n人件費の安い中国などに拠点が移り、日本が大量生産する時代は終わりましたが\n確かな技術と音に対する拘りで、有名ブランドの高級品の製造を請け負い\n様々なジャンルのギタリストを支えています。\n\n高級機にも劣らないしっかりとしたつくりと、フジゲン内で乾燥・管理されている良質な木材を使用し\nスタンダードでクセのない扱いやすさ、そしてフジゲンならではの木の鳴りを活かした音色を持ち\n抜群のコストパフォーマンスで大人気のネオクラシックシリーズ、エレキギターの原点ともいえるテレタイプが入荷！\n\nより正確な音程を目指し、各弦の誤差を修正したサークルフレット\nハイポジションまでスムーズでチョーキング時の音切れを改善したコンパウンドラジアス指板等\nフジゲンならではの技術力により一般的な弱点の多くが改善されており\n\nその構造上、よほど高価なモデルでない限り高域のみが目立ち、\n金属的なサウンドや音程とは関係のない高音域が耳を劈くモデルが多い中、\n木材の響きが活きた抜群の芯の太さと抜けの良さで低音まで充実しており\n煌びやかでキレのあるサウンドはもちろん、\nアコースティックなクリーンから厚みのあるドライブサウンドまで無理なくこなす\nジャンルを選ばない音色、弾き易さで初心者から上級者まで納得のクオリティーと扱いやすい音色です。\n\n\nBody : Alder\nNeck : Maple U-Shape\nFingerboard : Rosewood 250~350mmR Compound Radius\nScale : 25.5 (648mm)\nFrets : 22F Medium C.F.S.\nTuners : GOTOH® SD91-05M\nBridge : FGN TP-T6B (Brass Saddles)\nHardware Color : Chrome (Bridge) & Nickel\nPickup (Neck) : FGN 52T-HOT-F\nPickup (Bridge) : FGN 52T-HOT-R\nControls : 1Volume, 1Tone, 3-Way Lever SW\nFinish : Polyester\n\n\n付属品：純正ギグバッグ、正規保証書\n\nお問い合わせフリーダイヤル:0120-37-9630', 'FgN (FUJIGEN) NTL10RAL SWH New [Fujigen, Fuji string] [Domestic] [White, White, White] [Telecaster, Telecaster type] [Electric Guitar, Electric guitar]', 'Fujigen has been called the world\'s guitar factory for its long history and reliable quality.\nThe era of mass production in Japan is over, as the base has moved to China, where labor costs are low.\nWe undertake the manufacture of high-end products of famous brands with our commitment to reliable technology and sound.\nWe support guitarists of various genres.\n\nIt is as solid as a high-end machine and uses high-quality wood that is dried and managed in Fujigen.\nIt is standard and easy to handle, and has a tone that makes use of the sound of trees unique to Fujigen.\nThe neo-classical series, which is very popular for its outstanding cost performance, and the teletype, which can be said to be the origin of electric guitars, are in stock!\n\nCircle frets with corrected errors for each string, aiming for a more accurate pitch\nCompound radius fingerboard, etc. that is smooth up to the high position and improves sound interruption during choking\nMany of the general weaknesses have been improved by the technical capabilities unique to Fujigen.\n\nDue to its structure, only the high range stands out unless it is a very expensive model,\nWhile there are many models that listen to high frequencies that have nothing to do with metallic sounds or pitches,\nWith the outstanding thickness of the core and the goodness of pulling out, the sound of wood is alive, and the bass is enriched.\nNot to mention the gorgeous and sharp sound\nFrom acoustic clean to thick drive sound without difficulty\nIt is a tone that does not choose a genre, and is easy to play with a quality that is convincing for beginners to advanced players and easy to handle.\n\n\nBody: Alder\nNeck: Maple U-Shape\nFingerboard: Rosewood 250 ~ 350mmR Compound Radius\nScale: 25.5 (648mm)\nFrets: 22F Medium C.F.S.\nTuners: GOTOH® SD91-05M\nBridge: FGN TP-T6B (Brass Saddles)\nHardware Color: Chrome (Bridge) & Nickel\nPickup (Neck): FGN 52T-HOT-F\nPickup (Bridge): FGN 52T-HOT-R\nControls: 1Volume, 1Tone, 3-Way Lever SW\nFinish: Polyester\n\n\nAccessories: Genuine gig bag, regular warranty\n\nContact Toll Free: 0120-37-9630', 81840, '857', 'a:5:{i:0;s:80:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet-online/cabinet/fujigen/fgn_ntl_al_swh_body.jpg\";i:1;s:79:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet-online/cabinet/fujigen/fgn_ntl_al_swh_all.jpg\";i:2;s:80:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet-online/cabinet/fujigen/fgn_ntl_al_swh_back.jpg\";i:3;s:80:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet-online/cabinet/fujigen/fgn_ntl_al_swh_head.jpg\";i:4;s:78:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet-online/cabinet/fujigen/fgn_ntl_al_swh_fb.jpg\";}', '2021-09-04 02:40:01', '2021-09-04 19:46:58');
