(239, 3, 'https://item.rakuten.co.jp/guitarplanet-online/fgn-bil2-m-hs-tbs/', 'FgN(FUJIGEN) BIL2-M-HS TBS 新品[フジゲン][Blue,ブルー,青][テレキャスター,Telecaster][ギター,Guitar]', '日本製フジゲン、驚異のコストパフォーマンスを誇るテレキャスタータイプ入荷！\n\n国産エレキギター工場の代名詞でもあり、\n有名ブランドの下請け製造や、プロミュージシャンのオリジナルモデルを手掛け、\n海外でも非常に評価の高いフジゲン。\n驚異の低価格オリジナルモデル、Boundaryシリーズが登場!!\n\nテレキャスターを土台にしたシンプルなスタイルに、\nあっさりとしたクセのない響きを持つバスウッドボディーを採用\nフジゲンならではの本体の響きは低価格モデルでも健在です。\n\nフロントP.Uにはハムバッカーを採用し\nコイルタップスイッチとの組み合わせで多彩なサウンドメイクが可能\n高精度でしっかりとした造りに加え\nボディーバックやネックジョイント部分をの削り込みや\n弦高設定の幅が広いコンパウンドラジアス指板を採用し\n体格の小さな日本人にも抱えやすく、弾き易くなっており\nより安定したピッチを実現するサークルフレット\n各弦のオクターブ調整が可能な6駒ブリッジにより\nチューニングなどの安定感も申し分なく\n初心者にも安心して使いこなす事が出来る、\n高い完成度を誇っています。\n\nSpec\nBody:Basswood\nNeck:Maple U-Shape\nFingerboard:Maple\nScale:25.5 (648mm)\nFrets:22F Medium C.F.S.\nTuners:GOTOH® SD91-05M\nBridge:FGN FJIL-6SSTD\nHardware Color:Chrome & Nickel\nPickup:(Neck)FGN-BH-n (Bridge)FGN BIL-b\nControls:1Volume,1Tone w/Push-Pull SW(Tap),3WayLever SW\n\n\n付属品：純正ギグバッグ、正規保証書\n\n\n/_/_/_/♪出荷前調整ご要望承ります♪_/_/_/_/\nギタープラネットではご注文頂いた商品は\n新品中古問わず検品・調整してから出荷致します。\n弦高など細かなセッティング等、お好みに\n合わせて調整も可能ですで、お気兼ねなく\nお申し付けくださいませ。\n /_/_/_/_/_/_/_/_/_/_/_/_/_/_/_/_/_/_/_/_/_/_\n\nお問い合わせフリーダイヤル：0120-37-9630', 'FgN (FUJIGEN) BIL2-M-HS TBS New [Fujigen] [Blue, Blue, Blue] [Telecaster, Telecaster] [Guitar, Guitar]', 'Fujigen made in Japan, telecaster type boasting amazing cost performance is in stock!\n\nIt is also synonymous with domestic electric guitar factories,\nSubcontract manufacturing of famous brands and original models of professional musicians\nFujigen is highly evaluated overseas.\nAmazing low-priced original model, Boundary series is now available !!\n\nIn a simple style based on the Telecaster,\nAdopted a basswood body with a light and smooth sound\nThe sound of the main body unique to Fujigen is alive and well even in low-priced models.\n\nA humbucker is used for the front P.U.\nVarious sound make-up is possible in combination with a coil tap switch\nIn addition to high precision and solid construction\nShaving the body back and neck joint\nUses a compound radius fingerboard with a wide range of string height settings\nIt is easy for Japanese people with small physiques to hold and play.\nCircle frets for a more stable pitch\nWith a 6-piece bridge that can adjust the octave of each string\nA sense of stability such as tuning is also perfect\nEven beginners can use it with confidence,\nWe are proud of the high degree of perfection.\n\nSpec\nBody: Basswood\nNeck: Maple U-Shape\nFingerboard: Maple\nScale: 25.5 (648mm)\nFrets: 22F Medium C.F.S.\nTuners: GOTOH® SD91-05M\nBridge: FGN FJIL-6SSTD\nHardware Color: Chrome & Nickel\nPickup: (Neck) FGN-BH-n (Bridge) FGN BIL-b\nControls: 1Volume, 1Tone w / Push-Pull SW (Tap), 3WayLever SW\n\n\nAccessories: Genuine gig bag, regular warranty\n\n\n/ _ / _ / _ / ♪ We accept pre-shipment adjustment requests ♪ _ / _ / _ / _ /\nThe products you ordered on Guitar Planet\nWe will inspect and adjust the product before shipping, regardless of whether it is new or used.\nFine settings such as string height, etc. to your liking\nYou can also adjust it according to it, so don\'t hesitate.\nPlease tell us.\n / _ / _ / _ / _ / _ / _ / _ / _ / _ / _ / _ / _ / _ / _ / _ / _ / _ / _ / _ / _ / _ / _\n\nInquiry toll-free number: 0120-37-9630', 58960, '618', 'a:5:{i:0;s:76:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet-online/cabinet/fujigen/bil2-m-hs-tbs-4.jpg\";i:1;s:76:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet-online/cabinet/fujigen/bil2-m-hs-tbs-1.jpg\";i:2;s:76:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet-online/cabinet/fujigen/bil2-m-hs-tbs-2.jpg\";i:3;s:76:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet-online/cabinet/fujigen/bil2-m-hs-tbs-3.jpg\";i:4;s:76:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet-online/cabinet/fujigen/bil2-m-hs-tbs-5.jpg\";}', '2021-09-04 02:40:01', '2021-09-04 19:44:33'),
