(250, 3, 'https://item.rakuten.co.jp/guitarplanet-online/fgn_ntl11rmht_nat/', '【カタログ外モデル】FgN NTL11RMHT NT 新品[フジゲン,富士弦][国産][Natural,ナチュラル][Telecaster,TL,テレキャスター][エレキギター,Electric Guitar]', '国産ならではのつくりの良さと、老舗工場にしか出せない自然な鳴りで好評のフジゲン。\n独特のルックスと素晴らしい音色で高い人気を誇る、テレキャスターシンライン・タイプが入荷！\n指板にローズウッドを採用したカタログ外仕様です。\n\nテレキャスらしいメリハリ感、音抜けの良さはそのままに、マホガニーボディーとフロントハムバッキングの組み合わせは、よりふくよかで奥行きのあるサウンドをもたらし、よくある同仕様モデルのように埋もれることはありません。加えて、ローズ指板によりアタック感が落ち着き、まとまり良い扱い易さも実現しています。\n\nブルーズやジャズはもとより、シンプルで太いサウンドを活かしたロックでも大活躍の１本!!\n\nBody : Mahogany\nNeck : Maple\nFingerboard : Rosewood 250~350mmR Compound Radius\nScale : 25.5\" (648mm)\nFrets : 22F Medium C.F.S.\nTuners : GOTOHR SD91-05M\nBridge : FGN TP-T6B (Brass Saddles)\nHardware Color : Chrome (Bridge) & Nickel\nPickup (Neck) : FGN Alnico 8\nPickup (Bridge) : FGN 52T-HOT-R\nControls : 1Volume, 1Tone, 3-Way Lever SW\nFinish : Polyester\n\n\n付属品：純正ギグバッグ、正規保証書\n\nお問い合わせフリーダイヤル:0120-37-9630', '[Models not in the catalog] FgN NTL11RMHT NT New [Fujigen, Fuji string] [Domestic] [Natural, Natural] [Telecaster, TL, Telecaster] [Electric guitar]', 'Fujigen is popular for its good domestic production and natural sound that can only be produced at long-established factories.\nThe Telecaster Thinline type, which is very popular for its unique looks and wonderful tone, is in stock!\nIt is a non-catalog specification that uses rosewood for the fingerboard.\n\nThe combination of mahogany body and front humbucking brings a richer and deeper sound while maintaining the sharpness and sound omission that are typical of Telecaster, and it is not buried like the usual model of the same specification. In addition, the rose fingerboard calms the attack and makes it easy to handle.\n\nNot only blues and jazz, but also rock that makes use of simple and fat sound.\n\nBody: Mahogany\nNeck: Maple\nFingerboard: Rosewood 250 ~ 350mmR Compound Radius\nScale: 25.5 \"(648mm)\nFrets: 22F Medium C.F.S.\nTuners: GOTOHR SD91-05M\nBridge: FGN TP-T6B (Brass Saddles)\nHardware Color: Chrome (Bridge) & Nickel\nPickup (Neck): FGN Alnico 8\nPickup (Bridge): FGN 52T-HOT-R\nControls: 1Volume, 1Tone, 3-Way Lever SW\nFinish: Polyester\n\n\nAccessories: Genuine gig bag, regular warranty\n\nContact Toll Free: 0120-37-9630', 97680, '1024', 'a:5:{i:0;s:80:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet-online/cabinet/fujigen/ntl11r_mht_nat_body.jpg\";i:1;s:79:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet-online/cabinet/fujigen/ntl11r_mht_nat_all.jpg\";i:2;s:80:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet-online/cabinet/fujigen/ntl11r_mht_nat_side.jpg\";i:3;s:80:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet-online/cabinet/fujigen/ntl11r_mht_nat_back.jpg\";i:4;s:80:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet-online/cabinet/fujigen/ntl11r_mht_nat_head.jpg\";}', '2021-09-04 02:40:01', '2021-09-04 19:45:07');
