(257, 3, 'https://item.rakuten.co.jp/gakkiwatanabe/a110840/', 'Fender ( フェンダー ) Player Telecaster Black / Maple【MEX テレキャスター KH 】', '「Fender」ブランドながら手に取りやすい価格帯のPlayerシリーズが登場！\n初めての一本としても、2本目やサブとしても大変おすすめです！\n定番のアルダーボディ、メイプルネック、メイプル指板を採用。\nFenderの伝統的なルックスを踏襲しつつモダンプレイヤーのスタイルにもマッチするよう、\n近年様々なギターに搭載されることが多いミディアムジャンボフレットを採用したサテンフィニッシュのネックに\n少しパンチ力を加えたピックアップサウンド、伝統の3WAYサドルではなく6WAYのサドルを採用。\n22フレット仕様や“Modern C”シェイプネックなど、より実践的な演奏スタイルに即したまさに「プレイヤー」目線で製作された扱いやすいシリーズです。\nより手に取りやすく身近な存在になったFender。\n世界を代表するエレキギターブランドであなたのミュージックライフをスタートしてみませんか。\n大胆かつ革新的で、無骨なPlayer Telecasterは、ピュアなフェンダーと言えるでしょう。フィーリングとスタイル、そして最も大切なサウンドの三拍子揃ったこのギターは、囁きから、泣きのトーンまで思いのままに操ることができます。あらゆるスタイルに対応し、激しいプレイにも耐えうる丈夫さを備え、あなたの音楽的ビジョンを叶えてくれる頼もしい相棒となるでしょう。\nソフトケース付属\n他のサイトでも販売しています。買い物かごに入れても売り切れの場合がございますのであらかじめご了承下さいませ。\n \nBody Material Alder\nBody Finish Gloss Polyester\nNeck Material Maple\nNeck Finish Satin Urethane Finish on Back of Neck with Gloss Urethane Headstock Face\nNeck Shape Modern \"C\"\nScale Length 25.5\" (648 mm)\nFingerboard Material Maple\nFingerboard Radius 9.5\" (241 mm)\nNumber of Frets 22\nFret Size Medium Jumbo\nNut Material Synthetic Bone\nNut Width 1.650\" (42 mm)\nBridge Pickup Player Series Alnico 5 Tele® Single-Coil\nNeck Pickup Player Series Alnico 5 Tele Single-Coil\nControls  Master Volume, Master Tone\nBridge 6-Saddle String-Through-Body Tele® with Bent Steel Saddles', 'Fender Player Telecaster Black / Maple [MEX Telecaster KH]', 'Introducing the Player series in a price range that is easy to pick up despite the \"Fender\" brand!\nIt is highly recommended as the first one, as the second one or as a sub!\nUses the classic alder body, maple neck, and maple fingerboard.\nTo match the style of modern players while following the traditional looks of Fender\nSatin finish neck with medium jumbo frets that are often installed on various guitars in recent years\nA pickup sound with a little punch, and a 6-way saddle instead of the traditional 3-way saddle.\nAn easy-to-use series created from the \"player\'s point of view\" that is more in line with more practical playing styles, such as the 22-fret specification and the \"Modern C\" shape neck.\nFender has become more accessible and familiar.\nWhy don\'t you start your music life with the world\'s leading electric guitar brand?\nBold, innovative and rugged, the Player Telecaster is a pure fender. With a triple time signature of feel, style and most important sound, you can control everything from whispering to crying tones. Suitable for all styles, durable enough to withstand intense play, it will be a reliable companion to fulfill your musical vision.\nSoft case included\nIt is also sold on other sites. Please note that it may be sold out even if you put it in the shopping cart.\n\nBody Material Alder\nBody Finish Gloss Polyester\nNeck Material Maple\nNeck Finish Satin Urethane Finish on Back of Neck with Gloss Urethane Headstock Face\nNeck Shape Modern \"C\"\nScale Length 25.5 \"(648 mm)\nFingerboard Material Maple\nFingerboard Radius 9.5 \"(241 mm)\nNumber of Frets 22\nFret Size Medium Jumbo\nNut Material Synthetic Bone\nNut Width 1.650 \"(42 mm)\nBridge Pickup Player Series Alnico 5 Tele® Single-Coil\nNeck Pickup Player Series Alnico 5 Tele Single-Coil\nControls Master Volume, Master Tone\nBridge 6-Saddle String-Through-Body Tele® with Bent Steel Saddles', 69300, '726', 'a:5:{i:0;s:60:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/gakkiwatanabe/cabinet/online/64/618.jpg\";i:1;s:60:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/gakkiwatanabe/cabinet/online/64/619.jpg\";i:2;s:60:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/gakkiwatanabe/cabinet/online/64/617.jpg\";i:3;s:62:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/gakkiwatanabe/cabinet/online/101/1293.jpg\";i:4;s:62:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/gakkiwatanabe/cabinet/online/101/1294.jpg\";}', '2021-09-04 02:40:01', '2021-09-04 19:45:29'),
