(261, 3, 'https://item.rakuten.co.jp/guitarplanet/fender_player_telecaster_3cs_pf/', 'Fender Player Telecaster 3CS/Pau Ferro 新品[フェンダー][プレイヤー][Sunburst,サンバースト,木目][テレキャスター][Electric Guitar,エレキギター]', 'プレイヤーの新しい可能性を押し広げる2018年の新シリーズ「FENDER PLAYER」\n\nブランドの伝統と精神を受け継ぐPlayer Seriesは、真のFenderトーンとサウンドはもちろん、あらゆるスタイルにフィットするモダンな仕様を備えています。クオリティとパフォーマンスの両面において新たなベンチマークとなる本シリーズは、全モデルに共通のアルニコピックアップ、改良を加えたボディ、アップグレードされたブリッジ、鮮やかで大胆なカラーリング、トラディショナルなルックを演出する新デザインのクラシックロゴ等、ディティール面でも様々な面でアップグレードされています。\n\n\n[特長]\n・高品質材＆ハイコストパフォーマンス\n・弾きやすく、あらゆるプレイスタイルにフィットする\"モダンＣシェイプ・ネック\"\n・22ミディアム・ジャンボ・フレット採用\n・パワフルかつレスポンスの良い「Player Series Alnico 5」ピックアップ搭載\n・新デザインのクラシックロゴを採用\n\n\n[Spec]\nBody Material : Alder\nBody Finish : Gloss Polyester\nNeck : Maple, Modern “C”\nNeck Finish : Satin Urethane Finish on Back of Neck with Gloss Urethane Headstock Face (Pau Ferro)\n　　　　　　　Satin Urethane Finish on Back, Gloss Urethane Finish on Front (Maple)\nFingerboard :  Maple or Pau Ferro, 9.5” Radius (241 mm)\nFrets : 22, Medium Jumbo\nPosition Inlays : Black Dots (Maple), White Dots (Pau Ferro)\nNut (Material/Width) : Synthetic Bone, 1.650” (42 mm)\nTuning Machines : Standard Cast/Sealed\nScale Length : 25.5” (648 mm)\nBridge : 6-Saddle String-Through-Body Tele with Bent Steel Saddles\nPickguard : 3-Ply Parchment\nPickups : Player Series Alnico 5 Tele Single-Coil (Bridge/Neck)\nPickup Switching : 3-Position \nControls : Master Volume, Master Tone\nControl Knobs : Knurled Flat-Top\nHardware Finish : Nickel/Chrome\n\n\n付属品：純正ソフトケース、アーム、正規保証書\n\nお問い合わせフリーダイヤル:0120-37-9630', 'Fender Player Telecaster 3CS / Pau Ferro New [Fender] [Player] [Sunburst, Sunburst, Wood grain] [Telecaster] [Electric Guitar, Electric Guitar]', '2018 new series `` FENDER PLAYER\'\' that opens up new possibilities for players\n\nInheriting the brand\'s tradition and spirit, the Player Series features true Fender tones and sounds, as well as modern specifications to fit any style. A new benchmark in terms of both quality and performance, the series features an alnico pickup common to all models, an improved body, an upgraded bridge, vibrant and bold coloring, and a new design for a traditional look. It has been upgraded in various aspects such as the classic logo in terms of details.\n\n\n[Features]\n・ High quality materials & high cost performance\n-\"Modern C-shaped neck\" that is easy to play and fits any play style\n・ 22 medium jumbo frets adopted\n-Equipped with a powerful and responsive \"Player Series Alnico 5\" pickup\n・ Adopted a newly designed classic logo\n\n\n[Spec]\nBody Material: Alder\nBody Finish: Gloss Polyester\nNeck: Maple, Modern “C”\nNeck Finish: Satin Urethane Finish on Back of Neck with Gloss Urethane Headstock Face (Pau Ferro)\nSatin Urethane Finish on Back, Gloss Urethane Finish on Front (Maple)\nFingerboard: Maple or Pau Ferro, 9.5 ”Radius (241 mm)\nFrets: 22, Medium Jumbo\nPosition Inlays: Black Dots (Maple), White Dots (Pau Ferro)\nNut (Material / Width): Synthetic Bone, 1.650 ”(42 mm)\nTuning Machines: Standard Cast / Sealed\nScale Length: 25.5 ”(648 mm)\nBridge: 6-Saddle String-Through-Body Tele with Bent Steel Saddles\nPickguard: 3-Ply Parchment\nPickups: Player Series Alnico 5 Tele Single-Coil (Bridge / Neck)\nPickup Switching: 3-Position\nControls: Master Volume, Master Tone\nControl Knobs: Knurled Flat-Top\nHardware Finish: Nickel / Chrome\n\n\nAccessories: Genuine soft case, arm, regular warranty\n\nContact Toll Free: 0120-37-9630', 76230, '799', 'a:4:{i:0;s:75:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet/cabinet/fender_player/plyr_tl_3cs_all.jpg\";i:1;s:76:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet/cabinet/fender_player/plyr_tl_3cs_body.jpg\";i:2;s:76:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet/cabinet/fender_player/plyr_tl_3cs_back.jpg\";i:3;s:76:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet/cabinet/fender_player/plyr_tl_3cs_head.jpg\";}', '2021-09-04 02:40:01', '2021-09-04 19:45:42'),
(262, 3, 'https://item.rakuten.co.jp/guitarplanet/fgn_ntl11m_mht_tbl/', 'FgN NTL11M-MHT TBL 新品[フジゲン,富士弦][国産][シンライン][Telecaster,TL,テレキャスタータイプ][Blue,青][エレキギター,Electric Guitar][NTL11MMHT]', '国産ならではのつくりの良さと、\n老舗工場にしか出せない自然な鳴りで好評のフジゲン。\n独特のルックスと素晴らしい音色で高い人気を誇る、\nテレキャスターシンライン・タイプが入荷！\n\nテレキャスらしい立ち上がりと、音抜けの良さはそのままに、\nマホガニーボディーとフロントハムバッキングの組み合わせは、\nよりふくよかで奥行きのあるサウンドをもたらし、\nよくある同仕様モデルのように埋もれることはありません。\n\nブルーズやジャズはもとより、\nシンプルで太いサウンドを活かしたロックでも大活躍の１本!!\n\n\nBody : Mahogany\nNeck : Maple Soft V-Shape\nFingerboard : Maple 250~350mmR Compound Radius\nScale : 25.5\" (648mm)\nFrets : 22F Medium C.F.S.\nTuners : GOTOHR SD91-05M\nBridge : FGN TP-T6B (Brass Saddles)\nHardware Color : Chrome (Bridge) & Nickel\nPickup (Neck) : FGN Alnico 8\nPickup (Bridge) : FGN 52T-HOT-R\nControls : 1Volume, 1Tone, 3-Way Lever SW\nFinish : Polyester\n\n\n付属品：純正ギグバッグ、正規保証書\n\nお問い合わせフリーダイヤル:0120-37-9630', 'FgN NTL11M-MHT TBL New [Fujigen, Fuji string] [Domestic] [Thin line] [Telecaster, TL, Telecaster type] [Blue, Blue] [Electric guitar] [NTL11MMHT]', 'The goodness of domestic production and\nFujigen is popular for its natural sound that can only be produced at long-established factories.\nIt is very popular for its unique looks and wonderful tone.\nTelecaster thin line type is in stock!\n\nWith the Telecaster-like rise and good sound omission,\nThe combination of mahogany body and front humbucking\nBrings a richer and deeper sound,\nIt is not buried like a common model with the same specifications.\n\nNot to mention blues and jazz\nOne of the great success in rock that makes use of the simple and fat sound !!\n\n\nBody: Mahogany\nNeck: Maple Soft V-Shape\nFingerboard: Maple 250 ~ 350mmR Compound Radius\nScale: 25.5 \"(648mm)\nFrets: 22F Medium C.F.S.\nTuners: GOTOHR SD91-05M\nBridge: FGN TP-T6B (Brass Saddles)\nHardware Color: Chrome (Bridge) & Nickel\nPickup (Neck): FGN Alnico 8\nPickup (Bridge): FGN 52T-HOT-R\nControls: 1Volume, 1Tone, 3-Way Lever SW\nFinish: Polyester\n\n\nAccessories: Genuine gig bag