(265, 3, 'https://item.rakuten.co.jp/guitarplanet/fujigen-ntl10ral-swh/', 'FgN(FUJIGEN) NTL10RAL SWH 新品[フジゲン,富士弦][国産][White,ホワイト,白][Telecaster,テレキャスタータイプ][Electric Guitar,エレキギター]', '長い歴史と確かな品質で、世界のギター工場と呼ばれたフジゲン。\n人件費の安い中国などに拠点が移り、日本が大量生産する時代は終わりましたが\n確かな技術と音に対する拘りで、有名ブランドの高級品の製造を請け負い\n様々なジャンルのギタリストを支えています。\n\n高級機にも劣らないしっかりとしたつくりと、フジゲン内で乾燥・管理されている良質な木材を使用し\nスタンダードでクセのない扱いやすさ、そしてフジゲンならではの木の鳴りを活かした音色を持ち\n抜群のコストパフォーマンスで大人気のネオクラシックシリーズ、エレキギターの原点ともいえるテレタイプが入荷！\n\nより正確な音程を目指し、各弦の誤差を修正したサークルフレット\nハイポジションまでスムーズでチョーキング時の音切れを改善したコンパウンドラジアス指板等\nフジゲンならではの技術力により一般的な弱点の多くが改善されており\n\nその構造上、よほど高価なモデルでない限り高域のみが目立ち、\n金属的なサウンドや音程とは関係のない高音域が耳を劈くモデルが多い中、\n木材の響きが活きた抜群の芯の太さと抜けの良さで低音まで充実しており\n煌びやかでキレのあるサウンドはもちろん、\nアコースティックなクリーンから厚みのあるドライブサウンドまで無理なくこなす\nジャンルを選ばない音色、弾き易さで初心者から上級者まで納得のクオリティーと扱いやすい音色です。\n\n\nBody : Alder\nNeck : Maple U-Shape\nFingerboard : Rosewood 250~350mmR Compound Radius\nScale : 25.5 (648mm)\nFrets : 22F Medium C.F.S.\nTuners : GOTOH® SD91-05M\nBridge : FGN TP-T6B (Brass Saddles)\nHardware Color : Chrome (Bridge) & Nickel\nPickup (Neck) : FGN 52T-HOT-F\nPickup (Bridge) : FGN 52T-HOT-R\nControls : 1Volume, 1Tone, 3-Way Lever SW\nFinish : Polyester\n\n\n付属品：純正ギグバッグ、正規保証書\n\nお問い合わせフリーダイヤル:0120-37-9630', 'FgN (FUJIGEN) NTL10RAL SWH New [Fujigen, Fuji string] [Domestic] [White, White, White] [Telecaster, Telecaster type] [Electric Guitar, Electric guitar]', 'Fujigen has been called the world\'s guitar factory for its long history and reliable quality.\nThe era of mass production in Japan is over, as the base has moved to China, where labor costs are low.\nWe undertake the manufacture of high-end products of famous brands with our commitment to reliable technology and sound.\nWe support guitarists of various genres.\n\nIt is as solid as a high-end machine and uses high-quality wood that is dried and managed in Fujigen.\nIt is standard and easy to handle, and has a tone that makes use of the sound of trees unique to Fujigen.\nThe neo-classical series, which is very popular for its outstanding cost performance, and the teletype, which can be said to be the origin of electric guitars, are in stock!\n\nCircle frets with corrected errors for each string, aiming for a more accurate pitch\nCompound radius fingerboard, etc. that is smooth up to the high position and improves sound interruption during choking\nMany of the general weaknesses have been improved by the technical capabilities unique to Fujigen.\n\nDue to its structure, only the high range stands out unless it is a very expensive model,\nWhile there are many models that listen to high frequencies that have nothing to do with metallic sounds or pitches,\nWith the outstanding thickness of the core and the goodness of pulling out, the sound of wood is alive, and the bass is enriched.\nNot to mention the gorgeous and sharp sound\nFrom acoustic clean to thick drive sound without difficulty\nIt is a tone that does not choose a genre, and is easy to play with a quality that is convincing for beginners to advanced players and easy to handle.\n\n\nBody: Alder\nNeck: Maple U-Shape\nFingerboard: Rosewood 250 ~ 350mmR Compound Radius\nScale: 25.5 (648mm)\nFrets: 22F Medium C.F.S.\nTuners: GOTOH® SD91-05M\nBridge: FGN TP-T6B (Brass Saddles)\nHardware Color: Chrome (Bridge) & Nickel\nPickup (Neck): FGN 52T-HOT-F\nPickup (Bridge): FGN 52T-HOT-R\nControls: 1Volume, 1Tone, 3-Way Lever SW\nFinish: Polyester\n\n\nAccessories: Genuine gig bag, regular warranty\n\nContact Toll Free: 0120-37-9630', 81840, '857', 'a:5:{i:0;s:72:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet/cabinet/fujigen/fgn_ntl_al_swh_all.jpg\";i:1;s:73:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet/cabinet/fujigen/fgn_ntl_al_swh_body.jpg\";i:2;s:73:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet/cabinet/fujigen/fgn_ntl_al_swh_back.jpg\";i:3;s:73:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet/cabinet/fujigen/fgn_ntl_al_swh_head.jpg\";i:4;s:71:\"https://shop.r10s.jp/guitarplanet/cabinet/fujigen/fgn_ntl_al_swh_fb.jpg\";}', '2021-09-04 02:40:02', '2021-09-04 19:45:55'),
